snippet.title: Forgotten Hope - v0.6 Trailer(Short)
snippet.description:
A short preview video to version 0.6 of Forgotten Hope modification to Battlefield 1942 game.

*Please notice that the original audio have been swapped through Youtube's AudioSwap feature. Original audio was unfortunately blocked in many countries due to copyright issues (Thanks Sony Entertainment). But the music fits quite nicely!*

Check us out at http://www.fhmod.org
